name: Jacket Potato Beans & Avocado Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Preheat oven to 200Â°C. Scrub 6 potatoes to remove dirt. Dry with paper towel. Using a fork, pierce potato 5 or 6 times.
Place directly on oven shelf in the centre of oven. Bake for 50 to 60 minutes or until tender when a skewer is inserted into centre.
Cut a deep cross in the top of potato. Squeeze base gently to open.
Meanwhile, heat baked beans. Spoon over jacket potato. Add diced tomato, avocado, lime juice and coriander. Serve with lime wedge.
